answers.answer: Welcome to our community! Here is an article on what typical blood sugar numbers should be, in case it helps you. You can also find it in the Sugar Sense app (go to the bar menu in the upper left and select Health Guide, then scroll to the section Stay Well). If you find your numbers are out of healthy range, definitely see your doctor.http://www.medhelp.org/diabetes/articles/The-ABCs-of-Diabetes/2327
